If they move too quick

285
00:22:18,220 --> 00:22:19,250
(Oh whey oh)

286
00:22:19,250 --> 00:22:21,330
They're falling down like a domino.

287
00:22:21,570 --> 00:22:23,860
All the bazaar men by the Nile

288
00:22:23,910 --> 00:22:25,980
They got the money on a bet

289
00:22:26,230 --> 00:22:27,580
Gold crocodiles

290
00:22:27,680 --> 00:22:28,480
(Oh whey oh)

291
00:22:28,490 --> 00:22:30,600
They snap their teeth on your cigarette

292
00:22:30,900 --> 00:22:33,100
Foreign types with their hookah pipes say

293
00:22:33,120 --> 00:22:39,070
(Way oh way oh, ooh way oh way oh)

294
00:22:40,130 --> 00:22:42,310
Walk like an Egyptian

295
00:22:54,050 --> 00:22:56,520
The blond waitresses take their trays

296
00:22:56,550 --> 00:22:58,590
They spin around and they cross the floor

297
00:22:58,860 --> 00:23:00,180
They've got the moves

298
00:23:00,180 --> 00:23:01,160
(Oh whey oh)

299
00:23:01,200 --> 00:23:03,240
You drop your drink then they bring you more

300
00:23:03,500 --> 00:23:05,870
All the school kids so sick of books

301
00:23:05,870 --> 00:23:08,030
They like the punk and the metal band

302
00:23:08,190 --> 00:23:09,480
When the buzzer rings

303
00:23:09,500 --> 00:23:10,480
(Oh whey oh)

304
00:23:10,500 --> 00:23:12,650
They're walking like an Egyptian

305
00:23:12,830 --> 00:23:14,920
All the kids in the marketplace say

306
00:23:14,920 --> 00:23:21,420
(Ay oh whey oh, ay oh whey oh)

307
00:23:22,140 --> 00:23:24,570
Walk like an Egyptian.

308
00:23:28,120 --> 00:23:30,760
刚才遇到他了 他在厕所

309
00:23:30,880 --> 00:23:32,090
原来在厕所啊

310
00:23:32,190 --> 00:23:34,410
厕所就在门后面

311
00:23:34,470 --> 00:23:37,510
刚才好像听到了「蹲厕」什么的

312
00:23:38,150 --> 00:23:39,480
感觉我老是在厕所这种地方受到袭击啊

313
00:23:39,480 --> 00:23:41,470
正义 二
Justice